# REMI Navigation

## How to Run

```bash
uv run remi serve              # API on port 8000
uv run remi serve --reload     # with auto-reload
uv run remi <group> <command>  # CLI (groups: portfolio, operations, intelligence, ingestion)
```

Entry points:
- **API**: `src/remi/shell/api/main.py` → `create_app()` → `app`
- **CLI**: `src/remi/shell/cli/main.py` → `cli` Typer app
- **Script**: `pyproject.toml` → `remi = "remi.shell.cli.main:app"`

## Config

`load_settings()` in `shell/config/settings.py`. Order: `.env` → `config/${REMI_CONFIG_ENV}.yaml` → env vars.
Default is `base` (in-memory store, no DB required).

Required env vars: at least one of `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`, `OPENAI_API_KEY`, `GOOGLE_API_KEY`.
Optional: `DATABASE_URL` (for postgres backend), `REMI_API_URL` (sandbox CLI proxy).

## REST API — Actual Routes

All routes are prefixed with `/api/v1`.

| Group | Prefix | Key routes |
|---|---|---|
| Managers | `/managers` | `GET /managers`, `GET /managers/{id}/review`, `POST /managers`, `PATCH /managers/{id}`, `DELETE /managers/{id}`, `POST /managers/merge`, `POST /managers/{id}/assign` |
| Properties | `/properties` | `GET /properties`, `GET /properties/{id}`, `GET /properties/{id}/units`, `GET /properties/{id}/rent-roll` |
| Units | `/units` | `GET /units`, `POST /units`, `PATCH /units/{id}` |
| Owners | `/owners` | `GET /owners` |
| Leases | `/leases` | `GET /leases`, `GET /leases/expiring`, `POST /leases` |
| Maintenance | `/maintenance` | `GET /maintenance`, `GET /maintenance/summary` |
| Tenants | `/tenants` | `GET /tenants`, `GET /tenants/{id}` |
| Actions | `/actions` | `GET /actions/items`, `POST /actions/items` |
| Notes | `/notes` | `GET /notes`, `POST /notes`, `POST /notes/batch` |
| Dashboard | `/dashboard` | `GET /dashboard/overview`, `GET /dashboard/delinquency`, `GET /dashboard/vacancies`, `GET /dashboard/leases/expiring`, `GET /dashboard/needs-manager`, `GET /dashboard/trends/*` |
| Search | `/search` | `GET /search?q=...` |
| Knowledge | `/knowledge` | `POST /knowledge/assert`, `POST /knowledge/context` |
| Documents | `/documents` | `POST /documents/upload`, `GET /documents`, `GET /documents/{id}`, `GET /documents/{id}/rows` |
| Feed | `/feed` | `GET /feed` (polling), `WS /feed/ws` (push) |
| Agents | `/agents` | `POST /agents/{name}/ask` (NDJSON stream), session CRUD |

## CLI Commands

| Group | Commands |
|---|---|
| portfolio | `managers`, `properties`, `rent-roll`, `manager-review`, `rankings` |
| operations | `leases`, `maintenance`, `delinquency`, `expiring-leases`, `create-action`, `create-note` |
| intelligence | `dashboard`, `search`, `vacancies`, `trends`, `assert-fact`, `add-context` |
| ingestion | `upload`, `documents`, `document-search` |

## Where Things Live

| What | Where |
|---|---|
| DI container | `shell/config/container.py` |
| Settings | `shell/config/settings.py` |
| Capability registration | `shell/config/capabilities.py` |
| Domain schema | `shell/config/domain.yaml` |
| Agent manifests | `application/agents/*/app.yaml` |
| Unified query tool (20 ops) | `application/tools/query.py` |
| Document tools | `application/tools/documents.py` |
| Mutation tools | `application/tools/mutations.py` |
| Ingestion vocab | `application/ingestion/vocab.py` |
| Ingestion rules + authority | `application/ingestion/rules.py` |
| Ingestion entity persistence | `application/ingestion/operations.py` |
| Storage port | `application/core/protocols.py` |
| Domain models | `application/core/models/` |
| Portfolio resolvers + views | `application/portfolio/` |
| Operations resolvers + views | `application/operations/` |
| Intelligence resolvers + views | `application/intelligence/` |
| API routers | `application/{portfolio,operations,intelligence,ingestion}/api.py` |
| CLI commands | `application/{portfolio,operations,intelligence,ingestion}/cli.py` |

