## Testing

```bash
uv run pytest                    # all tests
uv run pytest -x                 # stop on first failure
uv run ruff check src/           # lint
```

## Demo Data Loading

```bash
scripts/load_demo_data.sh        # uploads all reports in correct order to running API
```
